1. *Išlo* je veoma teško, ali smo uspeli da završimo posao. (*Išlo* - It was very difficult, but we managed to finish the job.)
2. Oni su *išli* u šetnju posle večere. (*Išli* - They went for a walk after dinner.)
3. Kada sam bio mali, *išao* sam u balet. (*Išao* - When I was little, I took ballet lessons.)
4. Nismo znali kuda da *idemo*, pa smo se izgubili. (*Idemo* - We didn't know where to go, so we got lost.)
5. Kako je *išlo* na sastanku danas? (*Išlo* - How did the meeting go today?)
6. *Išao* sam kod lekara jer me boli grlo. (*Išao* - I went to the doctor because my throat hurts.)
7. Oni *idu* u Grčku na letovanje svake godine. (*Idu* - They go to Greece for vacation every year.)
8. Kako *ide* tvoj novi posao? (*Ide* - How is your new job going?)
9. Danas *idemo* u šoping, želim da kupim novu haljinu. (*Idemo* - Today we're going shopping, I want to buy a new dress.)
10. *Idi* odmah u svoju sobu i ne izlazi dok ti ne kažem. (*Idi* - Go to your room right now and don't come out until I tell you.)